          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Play Together, Stay Together: The Students SS24 Collection",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Golf is more than just a game; it's a journey—one that challenges us, frustrates us, and keeps us coming back for more. For many, it's not just about the score but about the camaraderie, the shared moments, and the endless pursuit of improvement. That's where Students comes in, a brand that understands the ups and downs of being a golfer and turns that passion into fashion.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
