    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Tribute to the Struggles and Joys of the Game",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This season, Students is bringing something fresh to the fairways with their SS24 collection, now available on TRENDYGOLF. The collection, themed \"Play Together, Stay Together,\" is all about celebrating the bond that golf creates among friends, even when the competition gets fierce. It's a reminder that while the game might test your patience, it also brings people together in ways that few other sports can.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
